{"root":{"data":{"text":"软件工程"},"children":[{"data":{"text":"软件工程定义"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dhoi5guwn9s0","created":1775725490887,"text":"由方法、工具和过程三个部分组成"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"dhoi5oka3hc0","created":1775725507658,"text":"PDCA（Plan、Do、Check、Action）"},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"text":"软件配置管理"},"children":[{"data":{"text":"前期准备"},"children":[{"data":{"text":"软件配置管理和版本管理(CMM)"},"children":[]},{"data":{"text":"记忆: 工程配置管理"},"children":[{"data":{"text":"配置标识"},"children":[]},{"data":{"text":"配置检查"},"children":[]},{"data":{"text":"配置审计"},"children":[]},{"data":{"text":"配置状态跟踪"},"children":[]},{"data":{"text":"版本发布管理"},"children":[]},{"data":{"text":"记录和报告配置项的变更, 可追踪和恢复版本"},"children":[]}]}]},{"data":{"text":"软件度量"},"children":[{"data":{"text":"软件工程量化"},"children":[]},{"data":{"text":"软件工程评估"},"children":[]},{"data":{"text":"能力成熟度模型CMM"},"children":[]},{"data":{"text":"能力成熟度模型集成CMMI"},"children":[{"data":{"text":"软件工程"},"children":[]}]}]}]},{"data":{"id":"dhoi6obiu6w0","created":1775725585493,"text":"软件开发方法"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dhoi6s8pvqw0","created":1775725594031,"text":"形式化方法"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dhoi6yv7iao0","created":1775725608451,"text":"净室软件工程CSE"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dhoi76pvgi80","created":1775725625543,"text":"函数理论（记忆：玩一阵）","note":null},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dhoi8c67cio0","created":1775725715778,"text":"完备性"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"dhoi8dqit2w0","created":1775725719184,"text":"一致性"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"dhoi8fh4se80","created":1775725722969,"text":"正确性"},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"dhoi7c5cwx40","created":1775725637363,"text":"抽样理论"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"dhoi8lblx740","created":1775725735696,"text":"限制"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dhoi8n3iio80","created":1775725739560,"text":"对工程师要求高"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"dhoi8p6awrc0","created":1775725744082,"text":"不依赖传统单元测试不实际"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"dhoi8w4921c0","created":1775725759196,"text":"属于传统软件工程体系，无法解决所有工程问题"},"children":[]}]}]}]},{"data":{"id":"dhoi97ptu7c0","created":1775725784445,"text":"逆向工程（记忆：世仇结、分工龄）"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dhoi9r2ub8g0","created":1775725826591,"text":"实现级"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dhoia696xb40","created":1775725859627,"text":"跟代码相关，比如抽象语法树、符号表等"},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"dhoi9tfra4g0","created":1775725831725,"text":"结构级"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dhoiaht5wjk0","created":1775725884779,"text":"跟程序分量相关，比如掉用途、结构图等"},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"dhoi9x2tgtc0","created":1775725839650,"text":"功能级"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dhoiap3zk9s0","created":1775725900671,"text":"程序段功能与程序段关系"},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"dhoi9zsscv40","created":1775725845574,"text":"领域级"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dhoib0uz48g0","created":1775725926247,"text":"程序实体与应用领域对应关系"},"children":[]}]}]},{"data":{"id":"dhoib8d1nl40","created":1775725942577,"text":"再工程"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dhoibazyem80","created":1775725948316,"text":"逆向工程 + 新需求 + 正向工程"},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"dhoibtr4hyo0","created":1775725989141,"text":"基于构建的软件工程（CBSE）"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dhoic2jytc00","created":1775726008299,"text":"特性（记忆：竹鼠挡毒标）"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dhoicezj36o0","created":1775726035362,"text":"可组装性"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dhoidh6ltns0","created":1775726118507,"text":"外部交互必须通过公开定义接口进行，必须提供对自身信息的外部访问，例如方法和属性"},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"dhoickvfcl40","created":1775726048174,"text":"可部署性"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dhoido6uvgo0","created":1775726133760,"text":"构件需要自包含，必须能作为一个独立的实体运行。总是二进制格式，无须在部署前编译。如果构建实现为一项服务，应由服务提供者来部署"},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"dhoicmzt4v40","created":1775726052793,"text":"文档化"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dhoidrh1zmg0","created":1775726140907,"text":"必须完全文档化，这样用户能确定是否构件满足需求，应定义所有接口的语法及语义"},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"dhoicoa42540","created":1775726055594,"text":"独立性"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dhoidu8jrhc0","created":1775726146923,"text":"可以在无其它特殊构件的情况下进行组装和部署"},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"dhoicocx3u80","created":1775726055762,"text":"标准化"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dhoie2636zc0","created":1775726164188,"text":"分支主题"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dhoie2dools0","created":1775726164648,"text":"构件必须符合某种标准化的构件模型，此模型定义构件接口、构件元数据、文档管理、组成以及部署"},"children":[]}]}]},{"data":{"id":"dhoicsl362g0","created":1775726064963,"text":"可见性"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dhoie570fh40","created":1775726170775,"text":"没有（外部）可见状态（两个特殊情况：1. 构件本身不直接暴露状态，但可以通过运行时容器管理状态并对外提供可见性；2. 对于不影响构件功能的某些属性可以对外部可见）"},"children":[]}]}]},{"data":{"id":"dhoie9vzcfs0","created":1775726180992,"text":"分类（记忆：独显时装秀）"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dhoieh48ylc0","created":1775726196729,"text":"分支主题"},"children":[]}]}]}]}]},"template":"default","theme":"fresh-blue","version":"1.4.43"}